  <brief_title>Study on the Effect of Intravenous Ascorbic Acid on Intraoperative Blood Loss in Women With Uterine Myoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Placebo-controlled,Doubled,Randomized Trial Evaluating the Effect of Intravenous Ascorbic Acid on Intraoperative Blood Loss in Women Undergoing Laparoscopic Myomectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
